OHMNI008 + OHMNI009 - Various Artists - Digitized Part 1 & 2
Omni Music, in conjunction with Digibeat Music, presents Digitized part 1 & 2. A varied collection paying homage to classic Digibeat releases, along with a sprinkling of exclusive unreleased pieces. Both volumes are testament to the high quality of the net labels output, with some of the most exciting artists in the underground drum and bass scene making appearances.
